	- Add String#get_1int and String#get_1float (see String#get_int and String#get_float)
	- Add String#get_ints and String#get_floats (see String#get_int and String#get_float)
	- Add Numeric#peer? and Numeric#odd?, add Integer#peer? too ;) (why no basic peer?)
	** Fixs **
	- Fix Array#average rounded dirty
	- Fix the String#get_float
	- Fix tests on String#get_float

